Package nl.pim16aap2.bigdoors.doortypes

Class DoorType

java.lang.Object
nl.pim16aap2.bigdoors.doortypes.DoorType
Direct Known Subclasses:
DoorTypeBigDoor, DoorTypeClock, DoorTypeDrawbridge, DoorTypeElevator, DoorTypeFlag, DoorTypeGarageDoor, DoorTypePortcullis, DoorTypeRevolvingDoor, DoorTypeSlidingDoor, DoorTypeWindmill
public abstract class DoorType extends Object
This class represents a type of Door. "Door" in this case, refers to any kind of animated object, so not necessarily a door.
Author:
Pim

  • Constructor Details

    • DoorType

      protected DoorType(String pluginName, String simpleName, int typeVersion, List<RotateDirection> validOpenDirections, String localizationKey)
      Constructs a new DoorType. Don't forget to also register it using DoorTypeManager.registerDoorType(DoorType).
      Parameters:
      pluginName - The name of the plugin that owns this DoorType.
      simpleName - The 'simple' name of this DoorType. E.g. "Flag", or "Windmill".
      typeVersion - The version of this DoorType. Note that changing the version results in a completely new DoorType, as far as the database is concerned. This fact can be used if the parameters of the constructor for this type need to be changed.
